{
  "texts": [
    "Instead, they should focus on skills that would enable students to address challenges utilizing AI technology (Pedro et al., 2019).",
    "Advancement in educational institutions has an impact on higher education and plays a key role in the growth of a nation, which has a reciprocal and dynamic impact on the social environment.",
    "All learning experiences can be learned with just one click to AI-assisted learning.",
    "Distance, time, space, availability of current learning materials, cost of trip, and risk of travel, just but few are no longer problems.",
    "Fast technological advancement is a sign that AI e-learning will inescapably play a part in raising the standard of higher education (Angib et al., 2022)."
  ]
}